query: Could you create a week-long travel itinerary for two people, departing from Fort Myers and planning to visit three cities in New York? Our trip is scheduled for March 11th to March 17th, 2022. We have set aside a budget of $5,400 for the entire journey. We would relish the opportunity to savor Mexican and Mediterranean cuisines during our trip.
